+# Slice 009D4: Readiness Effective-Role and Signature-Scope Closure
+
+## Status
+Not Started
+
+## Parent Epic
+Epic 009: SAP, Loan Account Creation, and Disbursement
+
+## Depends On
+- 008M7
+- 009D3
+
+## Runtime Capabilities
